{"tid":633611,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"發現自己好似有少少社交障礙","createTime":"2018-04-18T12:57:59.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-19T15:12:34.000Z","uid":177851,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"7b1655cab9f0a31f348f26ad247297d0a1efe065","tid":633611,"uid":177851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T12:57:59.000Z","msg":"面對啲唔熟既或者啱啱識<br />\n完全唔撚識點樣伸展話題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n成日人地講完我就笑住咁講：係啊 哈哈哈<br />\n尤其係面對着大過自己好多嘅長輩或者大5,6年咁樣<br />\n我真係好似自閉咁唔會主動搵話題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n淨係笑一笑咁敷衍下    好撚老尷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但岀奇地平時係班frd裡面<br />\n我通常都係搞氣氛個嗰<br />\n好撚極端啊屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n想問下如何可以係任何情況下都撘到嗲"},{"pid":"7beb9e3a5bcacf70b6ccde55343fa28df1c509c7","tid":633611,"uid":152047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T13:08:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我識咗半年都會咁"},{"pid":"9153081f709ed0fa9b5daa3c2e16f3a14234e9d9","tid":633611,"uid":177851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7beb9e3a5bcacf70b6ccde55343fa28df1c509c7","tid":633611,"uid":152047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T13:08:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我識咗半年都會咁"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T13:47:29.000Z","msg":"屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔明點解啲人乜9都撘到嘴"},{"pid":"3e66033e04b3799ae7fd40638e582ae342c4baca","tid":633611,"uid":82482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T14:06:34.000Z","msg":"me gum gum on bom"},{"pid":"269e5e53772c42b6df1056635cda900670477155","tid":633611,"uid":162910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T14:14:13.000Z","msg":"有冇諗過係長輩唔撩你講野？"},{"pid":"a0049874ba69ac72ba69cf284d6587f9344f697d","tid":633611,"uid":73575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T14:16:57.000Z","msg":"嚴重過你，無論長輩定同輩都係咁喎我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ccb2f61367f5e58d2902e3b516cffe869f10771","tid":633611,"uid":177851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"269e5e53772c42b6df1056635cda900670477155","tid":633611,"uid":162910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T14:14:13.000Z","msg":"有冇諗過係長輩唔撩你講野？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T14:40:20.000Z","msg":"通常都係佢地撩我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實我真係好想伸展個話題<br />\n但我好快就會講 係啊係囉係咩呢啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n搞到好似hea應"},{"pid":"1ccb904d2543ff62904c80d14aa72c6ecd038263","tid":633611,"uid":137912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T14:41:48.000Z","msg":"係啊 哈哈哈"},{"pid":"5f6311ec6ce4a243ec467c83d05120e6d8e571ce","tid":633611,"uid":153480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T14:50:36.000Z","msg":"平時睇多幾方面嘅嘢，體育音樂打機歷史又好，會容易啲打開話題<br />\n有次去旅行，發現外國人即使同你唔熟都會問吓你聽咩歌，有冇睇波咁，唔使咁拘謹<br />\n<br />\n同啲上一輩傾偈可以多啲問吓佢地啲人生經歷，佢地有威水史都會樂意講嘅<br />\n唔使咁快睇成係障礙嘅"},{"pid":"cf3ec4a1b3f135ee694c47b31a875962b23d5190","tid":633611,"uid":116364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T15:21:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"df0d122926487c919bc45e4c3aed7c7d5269a04b","tid":633611,"uid":116364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T15:23:37.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"17a05aacfb7420ffd8e0acd294a448a14b52801e","tid":633611,"uid":177851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cf3ec4a1b3f135ee694c47b31a875962b23d5190","tid":633611,"uid":116364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T15:21:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-19T15:12:03.000Z","